      A single, scrolling playbook built for students and employers.
      Add topics directly in GitHub. Each topic includes an <strong>Overview</strong>,
      your <strong>Approach</strong>, <strong>Evidence</strong> (screenshots), and a short <strong>Reflection</strong>.
    </p>

