      <span class="pill">Student-friendly</span>
      <span class="pill">Employer-ready</span>
      <span class="pill">No scripts required</span>
      <span class="pill">GitHub Pages</span>
    </div>

    <div class="callouts">
      <div class="callout">
        <h3>How to add a topic</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Open <em>index.html</em> ‚Üí Edit.</li>
          <li>Copy the <code>&lt;section class="topic"&gt;‚Ä¶&lt;/section&gt;</code> block (see below).</li>
          <li>Paste it under the right subject, then change titles/text.</li>
          <li>Upload screenshots to <code>assets/images/</code> and link them.</li>
          <li>Commit changes ‚Üí your site updates automatically.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="callout">
        <h3>Submission checklist</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Clearly titled topic section</li>
          <li>Overview ‚Üí Approach ‚Üí Evidence ‚Üí Reflection</li>
          <li>1‚Äì3 screenshots (named like <code>2025-11-lab2-01.png</code>)</li>
          <li>Share your live URL (GitHub Pages)</li>
        </ul>
